                        </li>
                     </ol>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d29e724" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph>   <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Change
order authority</i>. Contracting officers may authorize COR change
order authority in accordance with the limitations in GSAM <xref href="543.202.dita#GSAM_543_202"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">543.202</xref>,
Authority to issue change orders.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d29e740" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(e)</ph>  If
the HCA determines that the considerations listed under GSAM <xref href="542.302.dita#GSAM_542_302"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">542.302</xref>(c)
warrant the establishment of a contract administration office, a
contracting officer with an unlimited warrant may authorize contract
administrative functions in accordance with GSAM <xref href="542.302.dita#GSAM_542_302"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">542.302</xref>(d).</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
